{"tid":1872853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那口罩生產線能否於短期內復工？","createTime":"2020-02-10T09:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T10:33:57.000Z","uid":336588,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0a7497411798705e0de962dfa2fe68e296667eb4","tid":1872853,"uid":336588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:42:15.000Z","msg":"大家信唔信？反正我就不信了。<br />\n-------<br />\n新華網話，支那口罩最大產能是每天2000多萬隻，是世界最大的口罩生產和出口國，支那的年產量佔全球約50%。<br />\n<br />\n口罩短缺是因春節放假停產。相關生產企業絕大部分已停產放假，工人返鄉、原料停供、物流停運。一些工廠正在緊急擴大產能，但也需時間。廣東東莞的一家口罩生產廠負責人謝陽在接受采訪時稱，採購新設備、安裝調試，至少需要一個月的時間，新廠的機器要到三月底或四月初才能啟用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.xinhuanet.com/2020-01/30/c_1125512738.htm?fbclid=IwAR00ojKOl3fSdaYGnipY_v4udLSVp2XkL0pvN0eSdIR9NDoDAIY_6nHQjVc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xinhuanet.com%2F2020-01%2F30%2Fc_1125512738.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR00ojKOl3fSdaYGnipY_v4udLSVp2XkL0pvN0eSdIR9NDoDAIY_6nHQjVc&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVZKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=26974e28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.xinhuanet.com/2020-01/30/c_1125512738.htm?fbclid=IwAR00ojKOl3fSdaYGnipY_v4udLSVp2XkL0pvN0eSdIR9NDoDAIY_6nHQjVc</a>"},{"pid":"ad773d551fd7ce5ded31e6acee69f7b0bfe420b7","tid":1872853,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:44:04.000Z","msg":"二手口罩每日生產中"},{"pid":"197569bc2c3c1925a5c4b8870377be8fbc379613","tid":1872853,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:44:06.000Z","msg":"復工都唔敢用啦大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n生產過程已經咳咗啲病毒落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed76cbea48acb31b35228b632adf7b8e1b79e80e","tid":1872853,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T09:59:10.000Z","msg":"好得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw唔好意思阻你地討論sorrysorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i